{
  "openapi": "3.0.3",
  "info": {
    "title": "Kitajaga On-Demand Caregiver API",
    "description": "Dokumentasi API interaktif untuk backend aplikasi Kitajaga. Dibuat menggunakan spesifikasi OpenAPI 3.0 dan dirender dengan Scalar API Reference. Base URL untuk development lokal adalah `http://localhost:4000/api`.\n\n### 🌐 Panduan Integrasi WebSocket (Socket.IO)\nLayanan chat realtime & progress updates menggunakan protocol WebSocket (Socket.IO v4).\n\n#### 1. Koneksi\n* **Production URL**: `wss://be-kitajaga-production.up.railway.app` (gunakan port HTTPS standar 443)\n* **Lokal URL**: `ws://localhost:4000`\n* **Authentication**: Mengirimkan JWT token pada object `auth` atau header `token` saat handshake:\n  ```javascript\n  const socket = io(\"https://be-kitajaga-production.up.railway.app\", {\n    auth: {\n      token: \"jwt_token_di_sini\"\n    }\n  });\n  ```\n\n#### 2. Event: Client ➡️ Server\n* **`join_booking`**: Bergabung ke room chat booking tertentu.\n  * Payload: `bookingId` (string/uuid).\n* **`send_message`**: Mengirim pesan chat baru ke room.\n  * Payload:\n    ```json\n    {\n      \"bookingId\": \"uuid-booking\",\n      \"message\": \"Halo, saya sudah sampai\",\n      \"photoUrl\": \"optional-link-foto.jpg\"\n    }\n    ```\n\n#### 3. Event: Server ➡️ Client\n* **`new_message`**: Menerima chat message baru atau notifikasi sistem di room.\n  * **Payload Chat Message**:\n    ```json\n    {\n      \"id\": \"uuid-pesan\",\n      \"bookingId\": \"uuid-booking\",\n      \"senderId\": \"uuid-pengirim\",\n      \"senderRole\": \"user | caregiver\",\n      \"message\": \"Halo\",\n      \"photoUrl\": null,\n      \"sentAt\": \"2026-07-15T09:00:00Z\",\n      \"type\": \"text\"\n    }\n    ```\n  * **Payload System Progress Message** (Auto-generated saat caregiver update progress):\n    ```json\n    {\n      \"id\": \"uuid-pesan\",\n      \"bookingId\": \"uuid-booking\",\n      \"senderId\": \"system\",\n      \"senderRole\": \"system\",\n      \"message\": \"📍 Update: Caregiver menuju fasilitas kesehatan\",\n      \"photoUrl\": \"optional-link-foto-checkpoint.jpg\",\n      \"sentAt\": \"2026-07-15T09:05:00Z\",\n      \"type\": \"progress_update\",\n      \"meta\": {\n        \"status\": \"heading_to_facility\",\n        \"latitude\": -6.19,\n        \"longitude\": 106.84,\n        \"photoUrl\": \"optional-link-foto-checkpoint.jpg\"\n      }\n    }\n    ```\n* **`progress_update`**: Menerima data marker realtime (Leaflet map tracking).\n  * Payload:\n    ```json\n    {\n      \"bookingId\": \"uuid\",\n      \"status\": \"heading_to_facility\",\n      \"statusLabel\": \"Menuju fasilitas kesehatan\",\n      \"latitude\": -6.19,\n      \"longitude\": 106.84,\n      \"photoUrl\": \"optional-link-foto.jpg\",\n      \"createdAt\": \"2026-07-15T09:12:00Z\"\n    }\n    ```",
    "version": "1.0.0"
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "http://localhost:4000/api",
      "description": "Server Development Lokal"
    },
    {
      "url": "https://be-kitajaga-production.up.railway.app/api",
      "description": "Server Production (Railway)"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/auth/register": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "Pendaftaran User baru",
        "description": "Mendaftarkan pengguna baru dengan role `user` atau `caregiver`. Jika mendaftar sebagai `caregiver`, profil caregiver offline akan otomatis dibuat di database.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name", "email", "phone", "password", "role"],
                "properties": {
                  "name": { "type": "string", "example": "Zaki Ibrahim" },
                  "email": { "type": "string", "format": "email", "example": "zaki@mail.com" },
                  "phone": { "type": "string", "example": "081234567890" },
                  "password": { "type": "string", "example": "password123" },
                  "role": { "type": "string", "enum": ["user", "caregiver"], "example": "user" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Pendaftaran berhasil",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "success": { "type": "boolean", "example": true },
                    "data": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "id": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" },
                        "name": { "type": "string" },
                        "role": { "type": "string" },
                        "token": { "type": "string" }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/login": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "Login Pengguna (General)",
        "description": "Masuk ke sistem menggunakan email dan password untuk mendapatkan JWT token.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["email", "password"],
                "properties": {
                  "email": { "type": "string", "format": "email", "example": "zaki@mail.com" },
                  "password": { "type": "string", "example": "password123" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Login berhasil"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/login-user": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "Login khusus User Client",
        "description": "Helper endpoint khusus untuk mempermudah login User Client (Zaki Ibrahim) saat testing di Scalar.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["email", "password"],
                "properties": {
                  "email": { "type": "string", "format": "email", "example": "zaki@mail.com" },
                  "password": { "type": "string", "example": "password123" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Login berhasil"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/auth/login-caregiver": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Authentication"],
        "summary": "Login khusus Caregiver",
        "description": "Helper endpoint khusus untuk mempermudah login Caregiver (Suster Rina) saat testing di Scalar.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["email", "password"],
                "properties": {
                  "email": { "type": "string", "format": "email", "example": "rina@mail.com" },
                  "password": { "type": "string", "example": "password123" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Login berhasil"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/patients": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Patient Management"],
        "summary": "Membuat Data Pasien",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["name", "dateOfBirth", "gender", "address", "latitude", "longitude", "mobilityStatus", "emergencyContact"],
                "properties": {
                  "name": { "type": "string", "example": "Budi Santoso" },
                  "dateOfBirth": { "type": "string", "format": "date", "example": "1958-03-12" },
                  "gender": { "type": "string", "enum": ["male", "female"], "example": "male" },
                  "address": { "type": "string", "example": "Jl. Menteng Raya No.10, Jakarta" },
                  "latitude": { "type": "number", "example": -6.195 },
                  "longitude": { "type": "number", "example": 106.832 },
                  "mobilityStatus": { "type": "string", "enum": ["independent", "assisted", "wheelchair", "immobile", "bedridden"], "example": "assisted" },
                  "allergies": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" }, "example": ["Diabetes", "Debu"] },
                  "currentMedications": { "type": "array", "items": { "type": "string" }, "example": ["Metformin 500mg"] },
                  "patientNote": { "type": "string", "example": "Mengidap diabetes, sering lupa minum obat sore." },
                  "emergencyContact": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "required": ["name", "phone"],
                    "properties": {
                      "name": { "type": "string", "example": "Rina" },
                      "phone": { "type": "string", "example": "081298765432" }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Pasien berhasil dibuat",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "success": { "type": "boolean", "example": true },
                    "data": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "id": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Patient Management"],
        "summary": "Mengambil Daftar Pasien",
        "description": "Mengambil seluruh daftar pasien milik client user yang sedang login.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Daftar pasien ditemukan",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "success": { "type": "boolean", "example": true },
                    "data": {
                      "type": "array",
                      "items": {
                        "type": "object",
                        "properties": {
                          "id": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" },
                          "name": { "type": "string" }
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/patients/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Patient Management"],
        "summary": "Mengambil Detail Pasien",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Detail pasien ditemukan"
          }
        }
      },
      "patch": {
        "tags": ["Patient Management"],
        "summary": "Memperbarui Data Pasien",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "name": { "type": "string" },
                  "address": { "type": "string" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Pasien berhasil diperbarui"
          }
        }
      },
      "delete": {
        "tags": ["Patient Management"],
        "summary": "Menghapus Data Pasien",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Pasien berhasil dihapus"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Membuat Booking Baru",
        "description": "Membuat pemesanan caregiver on-demand. Tipe booking dapat berupa `immediate` (langsung dicari terdekat) atau `scheduled` (berjadwal). Ketika booking dibuat, Guidebook medis pasien otomatis ter-generate via OpenAI GPT.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["patientId", "bookingType"],
                "properties": {
                  "patientId": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid", "example": "patient-uuid-here" },
                  "bookingType": { "type": "string", "enum": ["immediate", "scheduled"], "example": "immediate" },
                  "scheduledAt": { "type": "string", "format": "date-time", "example": "2026-07-15T09:00:00Z" },
                  "facilityName": { "type": "string", "example": "RSCM Jakarta" },
                  "facilityAddress": { "type": "string", "example": "Jl. Diponegoro No.71, Jakarta" },
                  "facilityLatitude": { "type": "number", "example": -6.1865 },
                  "facilityLongitude": { "type": "number", "example": 106.8442 }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Booking berhasil dibuat"
          }
        }
      },
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Mengambil Daftar Booking",
        "description": "Mengambil daftar booking. Jika login sebagai `user`, mengembalikan daftar pemesanan milik user tersebut. Jika login sebagai `caregiver`, mengembalikan daftar tugas miliknya serta tawaran pekerjaan terdekat.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Daftar booking ditemukan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Detail Booking",
        "description": "Mengambil detail informasi booking. Respon disesuaikan secara otomatis berdasarkan role pengguna (User vs Caregiver).",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Detail booking ditemukan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/accept": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Menerima Booking (Caregiver Only)",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Booking berhasil diterima"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/reschedule": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Reschedule Booking",
        "description": "Mengajukan penjadwalan ulang secara manual. Caregiver aktif akan di-unassign dan Matching Engine akan otomatis mencari caregiver baru (mengabaikan caregiver lama).",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "reason": { "type": "string", "example": "Pasien memiliki jadwal mendadak" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Reschedule berhasil diproses"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/cancel": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Membatalkan Booking",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Booking berhasil dibatalkan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/chats": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Booking Management"],
        "summary": "Mengambil Riwayat Chat (Chat History)",
        "description": "Mengambil daftar seluruh riwayat pesan percakapan (termasuk update sistem progress) dari booking ini, diurutkan dari pesan terlama ke terbaru. Digunakan frontend untuk melakukan restore percakapan saat pertama kali membuka room chat.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Daftar riwayat chat berhasil ditemukan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/progress": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Progress Tracking"],
        "summary": "Mengirim Update Progress Checkpoint (Caregiver Only)",
        "description": "Mengirim data checkpoint aktivitas caregiver saat mengantar pasien. Status tertentu (`picked_up_patient`, `arrived_registration`, `in_consultation`, `completed`) wajib menyertakan URL foto bukti.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["status", "latitude", "longitude"],
                "properties": {
                  "status": { "type": "string", "enum": ["heading_to_patient", "picked_up_patient", "heading_to_facility", "arrived_registration", "waiting_in_queue", "in_consultation", "heading_back", "completed"], "example": "picked_up_patient" },
                  "latitude": { "type": "number", "example": -6.195 },
                  "longitude": { "type": "number", "example": 106.832 },
                  "note": { "type": "string", "example": "Pasien sudah masuk ke ambulans/mobil" },
                  "photoUrl": { "type": "string", "example": "http://photo.com/picked.jpg" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Progress checkpoint berhasil dicatat"
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Foto bukti wajib untuk status ini"
          }
        }
      },
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Progress Tracking"],
        "summary": "Mengambil Riwayat Progress Checkpoint",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Riwayat progress berhasil ditemukan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/report": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Report & Rating"],
        "summary": "Submit Laporan Medis (Caregiver Only)",
        "description": "Caregiver mengirim laporan medis akhir setelah selesai mengantar pasien. Status booking otomatis bergeser ke `reported`.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["notes", "conditionSummary"],
                "properties": {
                  "notes": { "type": "string", "example": "Obat sore sudah diberikan. Pasien perlu istirahat cukup." },
                  "conditionSummary": { "type": "string", "example": "Suhu tubuh 36.5C, tensi darah normal 120/80." }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Laporan medis berhasil dikirim"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/bookings/{id}/rate": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Report & Rating"],
        "summary": "Submit Rating & Review (User Only)",
        "description": "User memberikan rating dan review ulasan untuk caregiver. Pemicu otomatis proses **escrow payment release** (status pembayaran bergeser ke `released`). Profil rating rata-rata caregiver akan langsung diperbarui.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "id", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["rating"],
                "properties": {
                  "rating": { "type": "integer", "minimum": 1, "maximum": 5, "example": 5 },
                  "review": { "type": "string", "example": "Suster Rina sangat sabar dan tepat waktu." }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Rating berhasil disimpan dan escrow dana dicairkan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/payments/charge": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Payment Integration"],
        "summary": "Request Pembayaran Midtrans Snap",
        "description": "Membuat order tagihan pembayaran flat Rp 150.000 untuk booking tertentu. Mengembalikan token Snap Sandbox dan URL redirect pembayaran asli dari Midtrans.",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["bookingId"],
                "properties": {
                  "bookingId": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid", "example": "booking-uuid-here" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "201": {
            "description": "Snap token berhasil di-request"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/payments/webhook": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Payment Integration"],
        "summary": "Midtrans Payment Webhook",
        "description": "Callback endpoint yang dipanggil oleh server Midtrans untuk memperbarui status pembayaran (`settlement` -> `held` escrow). Verifikasi signature key SHA512 berjalan di endpoint ini.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Webhook berhasil diproses"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/payments/mock-settle": {
      "post": {
        "tags": ["Payment Integration"],
        "summary": "Bypass Pembayaran (Mock Settle Helper)",
        "description": "Helper API untuk mensimulasikan status pembayaran sukses (settlement) secara instan tanpa perlu memproses credit card/QRIS Midtrans asli atau mem-bypass signature key. Cocok digunakan saat demo/testing.",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": ["bookingId"],
                "properties": {
                  "bookingId": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid", "example": "booking-uuid-here" }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Pembayaran sukses disimulasikan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/payments/{bookingId}/status": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Payment Integration"],
        "summary": "Mengecek Status Pembayaran Escrow",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
          { "name": "bookingId", "in": "path", "required": true, "schema": { "type": "string", "format": "uuid" } }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Status pembayaran ditemukan"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/guidebooks/{bookingId}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": ["Guidebook AI"],
        "summary": "Mengambil Guidebook Medis Pasien",
        "security": [{ "bearerAuth": [] }],
        "parameters": [
